snippet.textDisplay: Ok I’m tired of all these comments trashing Matt to uplift Avi. Yes Matt is not a true bass but he has a wide range and he’s grown so much in these past two years. Also, to all the people saying ptx doesn’t sound the same without Avi... what did you expect?  It’s a different person with a different tone, different singing style, if they found someone with a similar tone to Avi y’all would be the same ones complaining that they’re trying too hard to replicate the sound they had with Avi.
